                android:layout_marginBottom="7dp"
                android:background="@drawable/custom_for_linear"
                android:text="Oh God, the house is your home, the slave is your slave, the son of your slave and the son of your female slave, you made me carry what you subjected to me of your creation,Until you led me through your country, and informed me of your grace until you helped me to perform your rites.If you are satisfied with me, then you will be more satisfied with me.If not, from now on, before your home is far from your home, it is time for me to leave."
